            <title>[HADOOP-6192] Shell.getUlimitMemoryCommand is tied to Map-Reduce</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6192</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently org.apache.hadoop.util.Shell.getUlimitMemoryCommand relies on a MAPREDUCE specific configuration property for the memory limit. We should break the link.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
